data.description: Remodeled and move-in ready! NEW flooring, NEW cabinets and counter tops inkitchen/baths. NEW fixtures. NEW interior/exterior paint. Community park with kids play area, basket ball courts, ramada & BBQ.Sellers are licensed real estate agents in Arizona.
